title: fanoutqa: Who are the nominees of the 2024 Taiwanese presidential election and what are their birth dates? (a8144c2b180759f1)

chat_history.content: Who are the nominees of the 2024 Taiwanese presidential election and what are their birth dates?

The 2024 Taiwanese presidential election will be held on 13 January 2024. The nominees are:

- Terry Gou - 18 October 1950
- Eric Chu - 7 June 1961

The incumbent president, Tsai Ing-wen, is barred from re-election by the Taiwanese constitution, which limits the number of terms a president can serve to two.
